{"tid":1392503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持前線！課金正確做法","createTime":"2019-07-31T18:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T18:50:09.000Z","uid":267038,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1e9917825b820375bf3adca1afbf96707b7882","tid":1392503,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:27:50.000Z","msg":"我P牌 可唔可以睇完先屌呀<br />\n<br />\n最近好多慈善活動<br />\n香港人嘅善心真係無法想像<br />\n香城online課金速度令人嘆為觀止<br />\n<br />\n不過唔好打飛機讚嘆自己嘅動員力住<br />\n<br />\n大家課咗金買禮物要送禮物㗎嘛<br />\n自己親手送禮物到現場係最好嘅支持！<br />\n<br />\n唔係一次過送哂啲禮物<br />\n而係每次帶少少去 <br />\n減低被敵軍截獲風險 而且到時先知邊個玩家要咩禮物<br />\n<br />\n好似畢業禮/表演/比賽咁 諗下如果你次次上台<br />\n家長都係買份玩具搵速遞送去就算<br />\n而唔嚟睇又唔親手送<br />\n咁咪成個場吉哂得返表演嘅細路 冇家長嘅支持？<br />\n<br />\n一次過俾哂啲禮物 咁下次咪冇囉？<br />\n<br />\n我希望各位善長仁翁可以親手送禮<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個玩家 一位善長 即刻多一倍人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最怕大家心裏面覺得做咗啲嘢 過咗自己嗰關<br />\n就唔再出現<br />\n人愈來愈少 就愈來愈難打"},{"pid":"37b5f3d44c38498b6a01ccc99f1ae3eeb366f455","tid":1392503,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"agger 前線最需要係人"},{"pid":"4bc50800273de81f146c8dded780fd73fcd88465","tid":1392503,"uid":68822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:28:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=856c49fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGGWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=d541f937\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3b70215723ae2b756d21e224e6170242faf4ef","tid":1392503,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T18:28:54.000Z","msg":"開錯台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係香城online玩家攻略<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77725f16238971f1784d5e7e6f94b3d1774fc418","tid":1392503,"uid":267038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"